= //<Dr. Deering and Dr. Reynders are arguing in the MAGIC DRAWER operations control room, which has been temporarily evacuated of all non-executive staff. Chief Torosyan-Deering enters, shutting the door behind her.>//

[[span class="ir"]]Dr. Reynders:[[/span]] Calm down.

[[span class="dd"]]Dr. Deering:[[/span]] No. Shut up.

[[span class="at"]]Chief Torosyan-Deering:[[/span]] What's going on? What's wrong with the report?

[[span class="ir"]]Dr. Reynders:[[/span]] MAGIC DRAWER is targeting us for delivery.

= //<Silence on recording.>//

[[span class="at"]]Chief Torosyan-Deering:[[/span]] What?

[[span class="dd"]]Dr. Deering:[[/span]] It's impossible. It is //fucking impossible.//

[[span class="at"]]Chief Torosyan-Deering:[[/span]] How can it be targeting... was it sabotage? Someone sabotaged MAGIC DRAWER?

[[span class="dd"]]Dr. Deering:[[/span]] That must be it. It's impossible. We can't be next, not after only //six// goddamn deployments!

[[span class="at"]]Chief Torosyan-Deering:[[/span]] There have to be safeguards for this kind of thing! Why can it even target a coherent timeline? It was designed to dump into pocket dimensions, it shouldn't...

[[span class="ir"]]Dr. Reynders:[[/span]] Amelia.

[[span class="at"]]Chief Torosyan-Deering:[[/span]] Dougall? It shouldn't...

[[span class="ir"]]Dr. Reynders:[[/span]] Amelia.

[[span class="at"]]Chief Torosyan-Deering:[[/span]] Oh, my god.

= //<Silence on recording.>//

[[span class="dd"]]Dr. Deering:[[/span]] So, here's the thing.
